metadata.description:
"Welcome to my Danger Zone" 

Danger Zone is the intro track from the Danger Zone EP, the genesis NFT collection from the Danger Zone DAO. Where Dorothy tells the story of the old, and I tell the story of the new. 

The project consists of seven songs, each with its own 7 Deadly Sin artwork. With this one being Greed, each sin represents a part of the song that, deep down, relates to a part of my life.

Performed by Ibn Inglor
Produced by Arran Sym
Additional Vocals by Arran Sym
Mixed by Arran Sym
Mastered by Collin Jordan

Hook
